                            <div class="carousel-item active text-center">
                                <img src="/images/client-01.jpg" class="center-block" alt="testimonial">
                                <div class="testimonial-caption">
                                    <h5>Elliot Olsson</h5>
                                    <h4>Tourist from Sweden</h4>
                                    <p>Since I started using Travelmos.com my trips to overseas countries became much easier and relaxed. All I need is to log in and send my request to a guide and in no time we're already working out our route.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
